title: John Rowe's college football picks - College Football
text:
Rowe’s picks 
Notre Dame (+2) against *Clemson — The Tigers have done a lot of talking this week. Let’s see if they can back it up.
*Georgia (-2) over Alabama — Usually don’t trust Georgia in big games, but this ’Bama team doesn’t look like past teams.
*UCLA (-13 1/2) over Arizona State — USC exploited Arizona State’s shortcomings. L.A.’s other team can do the same.
Play of the day 
*Wisconsin (-6 1/2) over Iowa — Few Big Ten road teams can stand up to the Badgers’ smash-mouth football.
Other games 
*Oklahoma (-6 1/2) over West Virginia; Mississippi (-6 1/2) over *Florida; *Mississippi State (+5 1/2) against Texas A&M; *Indiana (+22) against Ohio State
*home team
Last week: 2-6; Season: 11-21; Plays of the day: 1-3
